  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast includes a hot and cold buffet with freshly baked cakes, traditional Italian cheeses and English favourites. For guests staying on half board dinner is a choice of four courses, taken in the Dei Poeti restaurant.</p>
<p><strong>Dei Poeti Restaurant</strong> has wonderful views of the piazza and lakeside jetty. It's open for breakfast, lunch (payable locally) and dinner and serves Italian food made with fresh ingredients. </p>
<p>Choose from two bars to enjoy an afternoon or evening drink. One is located inside the hotel offering coffees and light snacks while the outdoor bar has a comfortable ambiance and refreshing cocktails. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
