  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sirmione's right on the lakefront in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba}" title="Sirmione">Sirmione</a>. That means the town’s cobbled streets, fairytale castle and gelaterie will be right on your doorstep. It’s been open since 1890 and is known for its spa. The sauna, whirlpool and sensory showers are wonderful after a day of exploring Sirmione.</p>
<h2>Aperol spritz with a view of Lake Garda</h2>
<p>You can’t stay here without enjoying a cocktail or two on the lakeside terrace. Pull up a chair next to the water and sip an Aperol Spritz as you watch the sunset. The views are amazing! Inside the décor is pretty modern and most rooms come with charming views over the piazza.</p>]]></description>
