  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Thermal Spa Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free entry to the thermal spa with steam baths, salt rooms, Turkish bath, sensory saunas, indoor relaxation area and terrace with lake views (these facilities are available to use in two hour time slots). From June-August the SPA facilities are available at any time, subject to availability. In May-September the spa facilities must be booked in advance*</li>
<li>Beauty treatments and massages (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><em>*From May-September you'll need to book your slot for the indoor spa area before you arrive to ensure you get the time slot you want. You can do this by calling the hotel on +39 030916331. This can also be booked locally, subject to available time slots.</em></p>
<p><strong>Hotel Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Small outdoor thermal pool heated to between 33-37<span>°C (pool opening is weather dependent and may be limited from October onwards).</span></li>
<li>Pool towels are provided</li>
<li>Discounted entry to Sirmione's Aquaria Thermal Spa (Mon-Thurs, payable locally)</li>
<li>Free hotel bike hire (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Lakeside terrace</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Grifo parking (400 metres away, must be pre-booked and payable locally for approx. €13 a day)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
